---
title: Gimbels' Santa Turkey Cheeseburgers with Caramelized Onions, Garlic Mayo and Cheesy Potato Snowballs
description: Unlike the mall Santa at Gimbels, this classic combo of turkey and cheese is the real deal. Enjoy juicy cheeseburgers on pillowy potato buns with garlic mayo and topped with balsamic caramelized onion. On the side are cheesy mashed potatoes you’ll roll into “snowballs,” coat in toasted panko breadcrumbs, then stack into potato snow-people. Who says you can’t play with your food? Not us!
